Text: mate, I updated my ipod touch 4G to a  4.3.5 not- jaibroken  firmware .....But after  knowing that its jailbreak hasn't been done, I downloaded your firmware.....I used iREB to go into pwnd mode.....and after it was successfully done, i tried shift+ restore from itunes......but it showed 3194 error............Any solutions to by-pass this error ?
3194 is SHSH error. You need your SHSH blobs backed up.
